Man AHL Evolution Frontier Ltd  Financing
Man AHL Evolution Frontier Ltd just submitted form D announcing  Indefinite financing.  This is a new filing. Man AHL Evolution Frontier Ltd was able to sell $21,000,000. The total private offering amount was Indefinite. The financing was made by 1 investors. Minimal accepted investment was $5,000,000. The financing document was filed on 2015-12-03. Man AHL Evolution Frontier Ltd is based in  CITCO TRUSTEES (CAYMAN) LIMITED 89 NEXUS WAY, CAMANA BAY GRAND CAYMAN KY1-1205. The firm's business is Pooled Investment Fund. The form was signed by  n/a AHL Partners LLP.





