Man Ahl Evolution Frontier Form D
The Cayman Islands-based Man Ahl Evolution Frontier Ltd filed Form D about $21.00 million offering. This is a new filing. The raised $21.00 million. The offering is still open. The total private offering amount amount was $21.00 million. The offering filing was filed on 2015-12-03. Man Ahl Evolution Frontier Ltd’s clarification was: Man Investments Inc. (“MII”) is an affiliate of AHL Partners LLP. The Issuer will not pay sales commissions to MII. MII compensates Registered Reps a salary and discretionary bonus, determined by many factors including assets raised for the Issuer.. 
 Man Ahl Evolution Frontier is based in Cayman Islands. The firm’s business is Pooled Investment Fund. The form was submitted by Jennifer Thomson Director of the Issuer. The company was incorporated in 2015. The filler’s address is: Citco Trustees (Cayman) Limited, 89 Nexus Way, Camana Bay, Grand Cayman, E9, Cayman Islands, Ky1-1205. Ahl Partners Llp is the related person in the form and it has address: Riverbank House, 2 Swan Lane, London, X0, United Kingdom, Ec4r 3Ad. Link to Man Ahl Evolution Frontier Filing: 000166008215000001.
Analysis of Man Ahl Evolution Frontier Offering
On average, startups in the Pooled Investment Fund sector, sell 37.80 % investment fund interests. Man Ahl Evolution Frontier sold 100.00 % of the offering. The average offering size is $24.76 million for companies in the Pooled Investment Fund industry sector. The total amount raised is 15.17 % smaller than the average for companies in the Pooled Investment Fund sector. 

